column2: SELECT TOP # A.ra,A.dec,A.objID,A.z,A.zerr,A.class,A.subClass,A.specobjID,A.specobjIDClean,D.oiii_#_flux,D.oiii_#_flux_err FROM   MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputCtrl AS A   OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( A.ra, A.dec, #/#.) AS B   LEFT INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS C ON B.objID=C.objID   LEFT INNER JOIN galSpecLine as D ON C.specObjID=D.specObjID INTO    MyDB.CTRLStellarMassGalSpecLine
